FIELD-O is a mobile-first B2B field commissioning and reporting platform.

The app is used by technicians, commissioning engineers, maintenance teams, and site supervisors.

The main goal is to convert field inspections into professional reports quickly with minimal typing.

Key product requirements:
- mobile-first
- bilingual English / Spanish
- minimal keyboard usage
- offline-capable draft workflow
- client-based report organization
- report preview before share
- professional PDF generation
- support for multiple equipment units in one report

Do not turn FIELD-O into a generic dashboard or generic form builder.
Preserve the field-use logic and industrial B2B purpose in all recommendations.

